msgid ""
"<Title>Your Bank ASEAN Account</>\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Balance:</> <Money>{balance:,}</>\n"
"<Small>Daily (IRL) Interest Rate: 2.2% (offline), 4.4% (online). Interest "
"reduces for balances above $10M.</>\n"
"<Bold>Loans:</> <Money>{loan_balance:,}</>\n"
"<Bold>Max Available Loan:</> <Money>{max_loan:,}</>\n"
"<Small>{max_loan_reason}</>\n"
"<Bold>Earnings Saving Rate:</> <Money>{saving_rate_pct:.0f}%</>\n"
"<Small>Use /set_saving_rate [percentage] to automatically set aside your "
"earnings into your account.</>\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"<Highlight>/set_saving_rate [percentage]</> - Automatically set aside your "
"earnings into your account\n"
"<Highlight>/withdraw [amount]</> - Withdraw from your bank account\n"
"<Highlight>/loan [amount]</> - Take out a loan\n"
"\n"
"How to Put Money in the Bank\n"
"<Secondary>Use the /set_saving_rate command to set how much you want to "
"save. It's 0 by default.</>\n"
"<Secondary>You can only fill your bank account by saving your earnings on "
"this server, not through direct deposits.</>\n"
"\n"
"How ASEAN Loans Works\n"
"<Secondary>Our loans have a flat one-off 10% fee, and you only have to repay "
"them when you make a profit.</>\n"
"<Secondary>The repayment will range from 10% to 80% of your income, "
"depending on the amount of loan you took.</>\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Latest Transactions</>\n"
"{transactions_str}\n"
msgstr ""
"<Title>Akun Bank ASEAN Anda</>\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Saldo:</> <Money>{balance:,}</>\n"
"<Small>Tingkat Bunga Harian (IRL): 2.2% (offline), 4.4% (online).</>\n"
"<Bold>Pinjaman:</> <Money>{loan_balance:,}</>\n"
"<Bold>Pinjaman Maksimal Tersedia:</> <Money>{max_loan:,}</>\n"
"<Small>{max_loan_reason}</>\n"
"<Bold>Tingkat Tabungan Penghasilan:</> <Money>{saving_rate_pct:.0f}%</>\n"
"<Small>Gunakan /set_saving_rate [persentase] untuk menyisihkan penghasilan "
"Anda ke akun Anda secara otomatis.</>\n"
"\n"
"Perintah:\n"
"<Highlight>/set_saving_rate [persentase]</> - Menyisihkan penghasilan Anda "
"ke akun Anda secara otomatis\n"
"<Highlight>/withdraw [jumlah]</> - Menarik dari akun bank Anda\n"
"<Highlight>/loan [jumlah]</> - Mengambil pinjaman\n"
"\n"
"Cara Menabung di Bank\n"
"<Secondary>Gunakan perintah /set_saving_rate untuk menetapkan seberapa "
"banyak yang ingin Anda simpan. Standarnya adalah 0.</>\n"
"<Secondary>Anda hanya dapat mengisi akun bank dengan menabung penghasilan "
"Anda di server ini, bukan melalui deposit langsung.</>\n"
"\n"
"Cara Kerja Pinjaman ASEAN\n"
"<Secondary>Pinjaman kami memiliki biaya datar sekali bayar sebesar 10%, dan "
"Anda hanya perlu melunasinya saat Anda mendapat keuntungan.</>\n"
"<Secondary>Pembayaran kembali berkisar dari 10% hingga 80% dari pendapatan "
"Anda, tergantung pada jumlah pinjaman yang Anda ambil.</>\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Transaksi Terbaru</>\n"
"{transactions_str}\n"

