#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"<Title>Burn</>\n"
"\n"
"To prevent any mishap, please read the following:\n"
"- This action is non-reversible\n"
"- Please do not burn more than your wallet balance! You will end up with "
"negative balance.\n"
"\n"
"If you wish to proceed, type the command again followed by the verification "
